----------------
Small slope, NE-ly aspect, in the shade of Jatzhorn. Snow depth about average. Representative for sheltered and calm areas.

PROFILE
-------
Ski penetration about 30 cm. Deep foot penetration. The snow hardness is low. Persistant weak layers failed.

RUTSCHBLOCK
-----------
The RB released at the third bend. It released below the skis.

PST 38/140 END @ 89 cm

SNOW SURFACE
------------
In calm areas the fresh snow (about 5 cm) has no cohesion.

SNOW DRIFT
----------
no fresh accumulation

ALARM SIGNS
-----------
No recent signs of instability observed.

AVALANCHES
----------
No new releases observed.</slf:text></slf:profiletext></slf:profiletext-list></caaml:customData></caaml:metaData><caaml:timeRef><caaml:recordTime><caaml:TimeInstant><caaml:timePosition>2023-02-07T11:30:00+01:00</caaml:timePosition></caaml:TimeInstant></caaml:recordTime><caaml:dateTimeReport>2023-02-07T15:07:26.176000+01:00</caaml:dateTimeReport><caaml:dateTimeLastEdit>2023-02-07T16:20:35.118000+01:00</caaml:dateTimeLastEdit></caaml:timeRef><caaml:srcRef/><caaml:locRef><caaml:name>Davos - Jakobshorn - Stillberg</caaml:name><caaml:validElevation><caaml:ElevationPosition uom="m"><caaml:position>2333</caaml:position></caaml:ElevationPosition></caaml:validElevation><caaml:validAspect><caaml:AspectPosition><caaml:position>NE</caaml:position></caaml:AspectPosition></caaml:validAspect><caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:SlopeAnglePosition uom="deg"><caaml:position>31</caaml:position></caaml:SlopeAnglePosition></caaml:validSlopeAngle><caaml:pointLocation><gml:Point id="pointID" srsName="urn:ogc:def:crs:OGC:1.3:CRS84" srsDimension="2"><gml:pos>9.859229 46.771191</gml:pos></gml:Point></caaml:pointLocation></caaml:locRef><caaml:snowProfileResultsOf><caaml:SnowProfileMeasurements dir="top down"><caaml:profileDepth uom="cm">123.0</caaml:profileDepth><caaml:weatherCond><caaml:airTempPres uom="degC">-10.0</caaml:airTempPres></caaml:weatherCond><caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:hS><caaml:Components><caaml:height uom="cm">123.0</caaml:height></caaml:Components></caaml:hS></caaml:snowPackCond><caaml:stratProfile><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">0.0</caaml:depthTop><caaml:thickness uom="cm">5.0</caaml:thickness><caaml:wetness uom="">D</caaml:wetness><caaml:grainFormPrimary>DF</caaml:grainFormPrimary><caaml:grainFormSecondary>PP</caaml:grainFormSecondary><caaml:grainSize uom="mm"><caaml:Components><caaml:avg>2.0</caaml:avg><caaml:avgMax>3.0</caaml:avgMax></caaml:Components></caaml:grainSize><caaml:hardness uom="">F</caaml:hardness></caaml:Layer><caaml:Layer><caaml:depthTop uom="cm">5.0</caaml:d